data.description: The search is finally over! Make yourself at home in this lovely 4-bedroom property in Sierra Montana. Discover a perfectly flowing layout showcasing neutral tile floor, soothing palette, soft carpet in all the right places, & arched doorways. The spotless eat-in kitchen features wood cabinetry, granite counters, track lighting, backsplash windows, built-in appliances, a convenient pantry, & a peninsula equipped with a breakfast bar. Primary bedroom offers a private bathroom with dual sinks & a walk-in closet. Spend relaxing afternoons in the spacious backyard including a pergola-style covered patio & plenty of space to hang out! What's not to like? Don't let this opportunity slip by!
